Title: Rose
Plot:
Location: London, England
Date: 4th/5th/6th March 2005
Enemy: Nestene Consciousness

Rose Tyler stumbles across a man called The Doctor as he seeks out the Nestene Consciousness, to prevent the living plastic it is controlling from taking over the world.
GuestStars: Camille Coduri, Adam McCoy, Elli Garnett, Mark Benton, Noel Clarke, Nicholas Briggs, Alan Ruscoe, Paul Kasey, David Sant, Elizabeth Fost, Helen Otway, Sarah K Chrispin
